1. License Grant
   The Developer grants the User a non-exclusive, non-transferable license
   to install and run the Software for personal or business use, subject
   to compliance with this EULA.

2. License Tiers
   - Free Trial: Free use for three (3) months from the date of initial
     installation. Use is terminated after the trial period. The following
     usage limits apply to the Free Trial and Beta tiers:
       · Up to 100 events
       · Up to 20 foreshadowings
       · Up to 20 characters
       · Up to 5 relationship-graph pages (excluding the default page)
       · Up to 20 collection items
   - Beta: Free use during the official open-beta period, subject to the
     same usage limits as the Free Trial.
   - Subscription: Monthly or annual billing. Usage limits are lifted for
     the duration of the valid subscription.
   - Permanent: One-time payment for perpetual use with usage limits
     lifted.

3. Payment and License Keys
   Payment processing and license-key issuance/validation are performed
